sequenceDiagram
    participant L as Local Brain
    participant S as Shared State
    participant E as External Brain

    Note over L,E: Append-Merge (score history, ledgers)

    L->>S: Append snapshot (scored_at=T1)
    E->>S: Append snapshot (scored_at=T2)
    L->>S: Read history
    S-->>L: [T1, T2] (merged, deduplicated)

    Note over L,E: Last-Writer-Wins (CMDBs, gates)

    L->>S: Write code-quality-cmdb.json (updated_at=T3)
    E->>S: Write ci-health-cmdb.json (updated_at=T4)
    Note right of S: Each domain has single owner<br/>Non-owner reads only

    Note over L,E: Event Protocol (optional)

    L->>S: Append event (score.updated)
    E->>S: Read events since last position
    S-->>E: [score.updated at T1]
    E->>S: Append event (ci.completed)
    L->>S: Read events since last position
    S-->>L: [ci.completed at T5]
